title: Hour 1 - Shaquille O'neal (05-08-20)
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Shaquille O'neal (05-08-20)
description:
Shaquille O'neal is a long time Dallas Cowboys Fan. Shaquille reminded Dan that his Orlando team is the only team to beat Michael Jordan in the playoffs after Michael had won a NBA title; he also reminded Dan that the next playoff season the bulls came back and the magic which sent him to the Lakers.
